==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Guadalcanal
<hw>Guadalcanal</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a mountainous
island; the largest of the Solomon Islands in the independent state that
is a member of the British Commonwealth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A battle in World War II in the Pacific (1942-1943),
in which American forces invaded the island of Guadalcanal, then
occupied by Japanese forces; the island was recaptured by American
forces after heavy fighting.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Guadalcanal.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Guaiac</ent>⟦br⟧
